Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Akihabara to all over the world!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Please remember us!\N{\fs}Per favore ci ricordi.
