Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirin! Risa! Nemu! Ei! Moga! Pinky!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dempagumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}d been bullied and shut myself away in my room
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The arcade was the only place where I felt like I fit in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My dreams had fallen apart, and I{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}d become desperate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But before I knew it, I was here smiling with everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The radio was my only friend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a horrible case of chuunibyou, and scared everyone away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I uploaded lots of odottemita videos to video{\fnVanilla\fs20}-{\fn\fs}sharing sites
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and stayed glued to my PC just for the views
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Living in the countryside, I{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}d always wanted to be like anime and manga characters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,50)}Akiba is my holy land, and here I live!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,0)}For the longest time, I{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}d played MMOs, never leaving my room
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my two hands weren{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}t enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,2000)}I used my feet to push the function keys
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even nobodies like us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,are now aiming big!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, make fun of us {\fnVanilla\fs20}-{\fn\fs} that{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}s just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}re long used to that {\fnVanilla\fs20}-{\fn\fs} go ahead!
