Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}ll someday take flight into the big, big, big, big world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}ll send everyone electifying dempa waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}s no limit to where we can go, we{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}ve got nothing to lose
