Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,With our unique style,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}ll win over the whole world!
