Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}s not about yourself, but about \Nsinging for the sake of someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dempa Big Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,0)}I didn{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}t want to go to school. I just played MMOs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Online, I{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}m not lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the same. I didn{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}t want to\Ntake a single step out of my room.
