Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}ve been a cosplayer ever since I was little!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The world of cosplaying was so cute and radiant, and I{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}d looked up to it.
