Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, I couldn{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}t do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Time went by, and I became a high{\fnVanilla\fs20}-{\fn\fs}schooler.
