Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,....are here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I had despaired over my powerlessness.\NI didn{\fnVanilla\fs20}'{\fn\fs}t know why I was in Akihabara...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There was this girl in the maid cafe I worked at.\NShe was really cute, and seemed so lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She put a huge smile on my face,\Neven with my wounded heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to help her out, even just a little.
